file.name: item.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Example API
paths:
  '/v1/items/{itemId}':
    get:
      operationId: getItem
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ItemId'
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/ItemResponse'
components:
  responses:
    ItemResponse:
      description: OK
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Item'
  schemas:
    Item:
      type: object
      properties:
        mandatoryInteger:
          type: integer
        mandatoryString:
          type: string
        mandatoryEnum:
          type: string
          enum:
            - 'one option'
            - 'another option'
        mandatoryDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
        mandatoryNullableDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
          nullable: true
        mandatoryFloat:
          type: number
          format: float
        mandatoryBoolean:
          type: boolean
        mandatoryArray:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        mandatoryObject:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/EmbeddedObject'
        mandatoryNullableObject:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/EmbeddedNullableObject'
        optionalInteger:
          type: integer
        optionalString:
          type: string
        optionalEnum:
          type: string
          enum:
            - 'one option'
            - 'another option'
        optionalDate:
          type: string
          format: 'date-time'
        optionalFloat:
          type: number
          format: float
        optionalBoolean:
          type: boolean
        optionalArray:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        optionalObject:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/EmbeddedObject'
      required:
        - mandatoryInteger
        - mandatoryString
        - mandatoryEnum
        - mandatoryDate
        - mandatoryNullableDate
        - mandatoryFloat
        - mandatoryBoolean
        - mandatoryArray
        - mandatoryObject
        - mandatoryNullableObject
    EmbeddedObject:
      type: object
      properties:
        string:
          type: string
    EmbeddedNullableObject:
      type: object
      nullable: true
      properties:
        string:
          type: string
  parameters:
    ItemId:
      in: path
      description: Id of a item.
      required: true
      name: itemId
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
        minimum: 0
